  "url": "https://www.lankadeepa.lk/latest_news/\u2019\u2019\u0dad\u0dd9\u0dbd\u0dca-\u0db4\u0dca\u200d\u0dbb\u0dc1\u0dca\u0db1\u0dba-\u0d89\u0dbd\u0dca\u0dbd\u0dcf\u0d9c\u0dd9\u0db1-\u0d9a\u0dd1\u0db8\u0d9a\u0dca\u2019\u2019/1-615717",
  "time_ut": 1656686705,
  "original_lang": "si",
  "original_title": "\u2019\u2019\u0dad\u0dd9\u0dbd\u0dca \u0db4\u0dca\u200d\u0dbb\u0dc1\u0dca\u0db1\u0dba \u0d89\u0dbd\u0dca\u0dbd\u0dcf\u0d9c\u0dd9\u0db1 \u0d9a\u0dd1\u0db8\u0d9a\u0dca\u2019\u2019",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "'' A meal asking for the oil issue ''",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Athuraliye Rathana Thera, Member of Parliament for our Jana Bala Party said that the oil crisis is a matter of demand alone.",
        "He said the rulers should intervene to expedite the appointment of a National Assembly and reach a broad consensus on the issues of the country, failing which the people would have to die or take to the streets.",
        "Ven. Rathana Thera stated this at a press conference held at the Sandaham Sevana Institute in Rajagiriya this morning (1).",
        "He said that he could not believe that the oil issue would be resolved next week and that the government had not yet made any statement in this regard.",
        "Rathana Thero who said that the government has been delaying this crisis for more than three months, said that it is a mystery why the plan was not made for three months when they knew this.",
        "He said that the rulers and officials had no idea about the use of oil and that the people as a nation should not face this misery.",
        "Ratana Thero said that this crisis was created by the rulers and said that these people who created the crisis have no right to become presidents and ministers.",
        "He also said that these people should accept the impossibility and go home.",
        "Ven. Rathana Thera said that the people could not bear the pressure any longer and accused the rulers of not preparing an important power generation plan for the country.",
        "They said it was possible to get oil from any country on humanitarian grounds and that some had plunged the whole country into crisis out of personal preference for fear that some would not be able to go and live in the United States with their children.",
        "He said that Iran had agreed to supply fuel for the country's tea and that he had told the President about it but had not received a successful response.",
        "In addition, the government has given up the opportunity to buy fuel from Russia, Ven. Rathana Thera pointed out.",
        "He said that two people are running this country together and this madness must end.",
        "Ven. Rathana Thera stated that this was not the karma of the whole nation and that the karma was imposed on the people by a group of karma makers.",
        "He said that this sin can be saved only if the Karumukkaras are chased away.",
        "Athuraliye Rathana Thera said that even if they are dragged to prisons on the road, they will not give up the fight and are not afraid to enjoy such results."
      ],
